{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"Iris_野丫头","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8LPhRVu5IDf7cEoBViauibf5fIttHgrsgiaiaNJo3Q5fDSj454yqUXeibewaZYyKAluuYWbBvu5HrITa/0","content":"<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">由于人民币潜在的贬值风险，敏感的投资者已经开始把目光转向海外投资产品。其中美元投资类产品门槛较高，在15万美元以上；外汇投资类产品投资周期较长，有项目退出和资金回流的风险；境外保险产品相对更加稳妥，香港保险尤其值得推荐。</span>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8661,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492697788000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"ZHIBIN","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLAMW8eic508AxKr4ribvyjbJOsAXBQkMXGXIh50MOV0ZGcliaqUibSogwjfMyJjRTAibhzFjPIcSvc4icGQ/0","content":"境外的资产的配置包括：外汇投资类产品（美元，房地产，股权），和境外保险产品。与中国内地居民而言，相对于外汇投资类产品门槛高、周期长，配置香港保险是最佳的选择。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8660,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492697756000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Candy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEjmF8gxz2kdlibUI1YvQDzrMCtduic8sFG8HlEibLAWfq2WTKwyMVBAYUibQx7icakRxg3euLUeAeicTibq/0","content":"<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">中国内地居民而言，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">投资美元存款和美元理财有助于资产保值，但如果只是短期持有美元，高昂的手续费可能抵消换汇收益。另外，美元投资的门槛以及对投资者能力要求都比较高，而外汇类投资产品周期又相对较长，只有境外保险产品相对与其他的理财产品而言比较稳妥一点。所以，配置香港保险无疑是最佳的选择。</span>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8648,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492695935000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"一粒尘埃","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM5aV6vKcBEuNlb