; &nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</div><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8615,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492692451000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jin","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEjDly006lpYzNjENQkTHHAlWxZbK8LGpe8kmNOYPUclDr5tiaqk6Nb0wPibKQgFkPEODH63NchSAUic/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">长期投资美元存款和美元理财有助于资产保值，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">对投资者把握外汇走势的能力要求较高。</span>不建议短期持有美元，因为高昂的手续费可能抵消换汇收益。</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">今年再次降息降准是小概率事件，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">把钱存在银行的收益赶不上CPI，相当于赔钱。</span></span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">海外投资产品中，美元投资类产品门槛较高一般15W美金以上，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">周期相对较长，加上<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">汇率波动因素，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">预期收益率普遍较国内理财产品低。</span></span></span><br></span></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">对内地居民，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">配置香港保险无疑是最佳的选择。</span></span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8540,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492682231000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title